\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Ps::2>Character Emotional State:<!$Scr_Ps::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Sarah:}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> A minor emergency whisks Sarah away at the beginning of the scene. <!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx331\li446\fi-86\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Evan:}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> Evan was feeling energized, inspired, and gratified. He was also happy to have found a new friend. A 14-year-old that reminded Evan of himself when he was that age. This relationship brought extra depth to Evan's emotions.<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Katie:}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> Katie was her usual upbeat self. Like Evan, Katie likes his new little buddy, Diego.<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Diego:}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> Diego was enjoying hanging out with Evan and the crew. Like Evan, Diego's father was not in his life. Nor does Diego have any brothers. Even though they just met, Evan and Diego bonded quickly.  Evan was like a father/big brother to Diego.<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 - Guido:}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> Guido was being Guido. Guido was doing a great job helping, but he didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t let a little thing like a day\u8217\'92s work get in his way of chasing women. With no success, he hits on Katie.<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_H::2><!$Scr_H::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Ps::2>POV: }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Third person limited, deep (focusing on Evan)<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\plain \f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf5
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf7 Dialogue Focus: }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Heavy<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\plain \f0\fs18\b0\i0\cf5
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf7 Use of Internal Dialogue: }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Moderate<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
